<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 08:11:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队在加沙汗尤尼斯发起地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-launches-ground-operation-in-gazas-khan-yunis/00000191-3608-de93-a799-7faf11be0000</link><description>在告诉一些居民撤离该城市一天后，以色列国防军宣布将第三次在汗尤尼斯开展行动</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-launches-ground-operation-in-gazas-khan-yunis/00000191-3608-de93-a799-7faf11be0000</guid></item><item><title>盗窃、殴打和无休止的骚扰：谁将成为这些定居者的下一个受害者？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theft-beatings-and-ceaseless-harassment-who-will-be-these-settlers-next-victim/00000191-31cf-dedb-abb7-77ef54ce0000</link><description>一位 62 岁的祖母和她的侄子在南希伯伦山遭到殴打。他们的七只羊被偷了。一名外国活动人士的护照被没收。十个月来，几乎每天都有定居者袭击无助的巴勒斯坦牧羊人</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:34:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theft-beatings-and-ceaseless-harassment-who-will-be-these-settlers-next-victim/00000191-31cf-dedb-abb7-77ef54ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的敌人寻求报复，但不会严厉到发动全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-enemies-seek-revenge-but-not-so-harsh-as-to-start-all-out-war/00000191-32f0-d2d3-af9d-3ef5c6750000</link><description>以色列公众正在认真对待伊朗和真主党对国内前线发动导弹和无人机袭击的威胁，内塔尼亚胡不愿意做出使战争更接近结束的协议所需的妥协</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-enemies-seek-revenge-but-not-so-harsh-as-to-start-all-out-war/00000191-32f0-d2d3-af9d-3ef5c6750000</guid></item><item><title>当内塔尼亚胡等待特朗普时，以色列的拆除人员政府破坏了西方的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/while-netanyahu-waits-for-trump-israels-demolition-crew-govt-undermines-western-support/00000191-33a6-daa8-a3b7-f7f7d2340000</link><description>以色列在发动多线战争时有三种选择，但总理宁愿推迟 ■ 流行的迟到 308 天，内塔尼亚胡记得为 10 月 7 日道歉 - 但仅限英语</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:00:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/while-netanyahu-waits-for-trump-israels-demolition-crew-govt-undermines-western-support/00000191-33a6-daa8-a3b7-f7f7d2340000</guid></item><item><title>火箭弹袭击以色列北部；报告：黎巴嫩无人机袭击造成两人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article-live/senior-u-s-official-no-expectation-gaza-deal-will-be-signed-when-sides-meet-next-week/00000191-34b3-d2d3-af9d-3cb7c54c0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布开始在加沙南部汗尤尼斯开展地面行动 ■ 两名人质的母亲表示，她从他们那里收到了生命迹象 ■ 美国、埃及和卡塔尔称加沙框架协议已敲定；以色列同意于 8 月 15 日派遣代表团 ■ 以色列国防军军官在加沙受伤 ■ 国防部长奥斯汀致 Gallant：美国致力于阻止侵略、保卫以色列</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:22:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article-live/senior-u-s-official-no-expectation-gaza-deal-will-be-signed-when-sides-meet-next-week/00000191-34b3-d2d3-af9d-3cb7c54c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将派代表团“敲定”加沙停火和人质协议；会谈将于8月15日举行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-send-team-to-finalize-gaza-cease-fire-hostage-deal-talks-to-be-held-aug-15/00000191-340c-dd83-a9bb-759ecac30000</link><description>美国、埃及和卡塔尔领导人邀请以色列和哈马斯参加多哈或开罗会谈后，美国高级官员：预计周四不会签署协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 22:27:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-send-team-to-finalize-gaza-cease-fire-hostage-deal-talks-to-be-held-aug-15/00000191-340c-dd83-a9bb-759ecac30000</guid></item><item><title>哈德拉警察局长因袭击事件接受调查，也涉嫌妨碍调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/hadera-police-chief-under-investigation-for-assault-also-suspected-of-obstructing-probe/00000191-3337-d6fe-a9fd-33bf18be0000</link><description>司法部调查人员表示，总警司阿米特·波拉克 (Amit Pollak) 本周因 4 月份在内塔尼亚胡家外暴力逮捕老年抗议者而受到讯问，他还就手机损坏问题撒了谎。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:24:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-09/ty-article/.premium/hadera-police-chief-under-investigation-for-assault-also-suspected-of-obstructing-probe/00000191-3337-d6fe-a9fd-33bf18be0000</guid></item><item><title>打开电视就可以看到以色列自 10 月 7 日以来道德的恶化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-09/ty-article/.highlight/to-see-israels-moral-deterioration-since-october-7-just-turn-on-your-television/00000191-3272-de61-adb5-b27e20cc0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡和他的盟友将作为亵渎以色列社会以推进民族主义弥赛亚议程的人而载入史册。像第 12 频道新闻首席执行官阿维·韦斯这样的人物将因教唆这场毁灭而被埋葬，不是因为意识形态，而是因为对收视率的不懈追求</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-09/ty-article/.highlight/to-see-israels-moral-deterioration-since-october-7-just-turn-on-your-television/00000191-3272-de61-adb5-b27e20cc0000</guid></item><item><title>“之前我因为安全局势而放弃了一次以色列之行。我没有时间再等了&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-08/ty-article/.highlight/i-passed-up-a-trip-to-israel-because-of-war-once-before-i-have-no-more-time-to-wait/00000191-3388-daa8-a3b7-f7dff71c0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对父子去朝圣，参观圣地并品尝 Shakshuka，一名匈牙利侨民向以色列的新移民传达了令人鼓舞的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:18:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-08/ty-article/.highlight/i-passed-up-a-trip-to-israel-because-of-war-once-before-i-have-no-more-time-to-wait/00000191-3388-daa8-a3b7-f7dff71c0000</guid></item><item><title>“他们的头顶上没有屋顶”：数千名加沙人逃离汗尤尼斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/left-without-a-roof-over-their-heads-thousands-of-gazans-flee-khan-yunis/00000191-337c-d2d3-af9d-3ffdd2140000</link><description>以色列军队再次呼吁汗尤尼斯许多社区的居民前往马瓦西安全区。加沙紧急服务部门称，以色列周四袭击了舒贾耶两所学校，造成至少 15 人死亡，至少 30 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/left-without-a-roof-over-their-heads-thousands-of-gazans-flee-khan-yunis/00000191-337c-d2d3-af9d-3ffdd2140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列废弃北部天空的观察者在真主党的无人机下创作艺术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/watcher-of-the-skies-of-israels-abandoned-north-creates-art-under-hezbollahs-drones/00000191-32d5-dd83-a9bb-73df570d0000</link><description>在海法艺术博物馆，艺术家哈达尔·赛凡 (Hadar Saifan) 为一个孤独的地区发声。此外，一部纪录片讲述了诺瓦音乐节的悲惨故事，一本新书探讨了战时的女权主义</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:17:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/watcher-of-the-skies-of-israels-abandoned-north-creates-art-under-hezbollahs-drones/00000191-32d5-dd83-a9bb-73df570d0000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯世界在社交媒体上赞扬叶海亚·辛瓦尔登上哈马斯的最高宝座</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/on-x-arab-world-praises-sinwars-ascendancy-to-hamas-top-spot/00000191-31e4-d18b-a1b1-f3e7e1930000</link><description>随着长达10个月的加沙战争的持续，强硬派被认为是一个不错的选择，但一些评论员担心，此举让这位10月7日建筑师有更大的许可与以色列“战斗到最后一个孩子”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 18:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/on-x-arab-world-praises-sinwars-ascendancy-to-hamas-top-spot/00000191-31e4-d18b-a1b1-f3e7e1930000</guid></item><item><title>纳粹德国的犹太共产主义者、犹太复国主义者和反犹太复国主义者：艺术家莉亚·格伦迪格的一生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/jewish-communist-in-nazi-germany-zionist-and-anti-zionist-the-life-of-artist-lea-grundig/00000191-331d-d940-a991-f7df832c0000</link><description>在新兴以色列事业蓬勃发展的鼎盛时期，蜚声国际的犹太裔德国画家莉亚·格伦迪格 (Lea Grundig) 抛下一切回到了东德，在那里他的光芒逐渐褪去。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 18:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/jewish-communist-in-nazi-germany-zionist-and-anti-zionist-the-life-of-artist-lea-grundig/00000191-331d-d940-a991-f7df832c0000</guid></item><item><title>奇迹产业：10 月 7 日之后，谁会从超自然故事的扩散中受益？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/industry-of-miracles-who-benefits-from-the-supernatural-tales-proliferating-after-oct-7/00000191-326b-d2d3-af9d-3eff46940000</link><description>奈蒂沃特是否因三个正义之人出现在恐怖分子面前而免遭屠杀？ 10 月 7 日的破裂催生了数百个关于奇迹和救赎的故事，证明了需要从混乱中创造意义——当然还有一些人希望利用这种情况</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 17:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/industry-of-miracles-who-benefits-from-the-supernatural-tales-proliferating-after-oct-7/00000191-326b-d2d3-af9d-3eff46940000</guid></item><item><title>对于哈里斯来说，蒂姆·沃尔兹对以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的沉默是一笔财富</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/for-harris-tim-walzs-silence-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict-is-an-asset/00000191-315f-d3fe-adf5-397fce150000</link><description>卡马拉·哈里斯选择明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹作为副总统人选，这表明民主党明智地优先考虑反特朗普选民的注意力，而不是亲巴勒斯坦选民的注意力</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/for-harris-tim-walzs-silence-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict-is-an-asset/00000191-315f-d3fe-adf5-397fce150000</guid></item><item><title>敏感基地的以色列士兵如何透露他们的身份和位置</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-at-sensitive-security-sites-reveal-their-identity-and-location-online/00000191-326a-d9ba-a5df-7a7b855a0000</link><description>《国土报》的一项调查：以色列国防军努力执行行动安全规定，尽管有关于智能手机和智能手表的明确指示，但敏感信息正在泄露并很容易被敌人获取</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:07:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-at-sensitive-security-sites-reveal-their-identity-and-location-online/00000191-326a-d9ba-a5df-7a7b855a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方继续没收反战抗议标语，尽管一再下令不要这样做</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-continue-confiscating-anti-war-protest-signs-despite-repeated-orders-not-to/00000191-3249-dedb-abb7-7769e0ee0000</link><description>国家检察官办公室表示，禁止扣押政治标牌的命令已广泛传阅六次，但均被忽视</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-continue-confiscating-anti-war-protest-signs-despite-repeated-orders-not-to/00000191-3249-dedb-abb7-7769e0ee0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉《时代》杂志，他对 10 月 7 日事件感到“抱歉”，现在“不是提出问责问题的时候”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/netanyahu-tells-time-hes-sorry-for-oct-7-now-not-the-time-to-accept-accountability/00000191-3238-d2d3-af9d-3ebda9430000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡表示，加沙战争结束后，将成立一个“独立委员会，对10月7日之前发生的一切进行审查”，并且“每个人都必须回答一些棘手的问题，包括我”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/netanyahu-tells-time-hes-sorry-for-oct-7-now-not-the-time-to-accept-accountability/00000191-3238-d2d3-af9d-3ebda9430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备应对极右翼部长关于饿死加沙人的言论的后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-for-fallout-of-far-right-ministers-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-31dc-d7be-a395-33fe6eb70001</link><description>欧盟国家、英国和其他国家谴责右翼部长的“令人震惊和有害的言论”，他表示国际压力是以色列没有饿死加沙人的唯一原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-for-fallout-of-far-right-ministers-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-31dc-d7be-a395-33fe6eb70001</guid></item><item><title>英文维基百科编辑总结：以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/english-wikipedia-editors-concluded-israel-is-committing-genocide-in-gaza/00000191-321a-d4dc-a397-bf1e3fba0000</link><description>自从世界上最受欢迎的在线网站的编辑上个月投票决定将维基百科条目重命名为“加沙种族灭绝”并删除了之前的“指控”一词以来，该条目每天都有数以万计的浏览量</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:43:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/english-wikipedia-editors-concluded-israel-is-committing-genocide-in-gaza/00000191-321a-d4dc-a397-bf1e3fba0000</guid></item></channel></rss>